      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>bread roll[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Once the <strong>potatoes</strong> have cooked, remove the tray[s] from the oven and push the potatoes to one side</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced bread</strong> to the other side of the baking tray[s], then return the tray[s] to the oven for 5-6 min or until the bread is starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
