      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a small pot with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once the butter has melted, add the <strong>chopped chives </strong>and<strong> </strong>the<strong> chopped mackerel </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min or until warmed through – this is your <strong>buttery chive mackerel</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
