    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build, spread the <strong>roasted garlic mayo</strong> on each<strong> toasted bread roll half</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>cooked potato discs</strong>, a <strong>lettuce leaf</strong>, the <strong>remaining sliced cucumber</strong>, <strong>buttery chive mackerel </strong>and your <strong>crispy onions</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>dressed salad </strong>to one side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
